== Deaths == * [[:en:Ten'ei|Tennen]] 2nd year ([[Julian calendar]] [[1111]] [[December 7]]） – [[:en:Ōe no Masafusa|Ōe Masafusa]], a kugyō, Confucian scholar, and poet (born [[1041]]). * [[:en:Genkyū|Genkyū]] 1st year ([[Julian calendar]] [[1204]] [[November 27]]） – {{ill|Hojo Masanori|ja|北条政範|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Masanori|qq=}}, a military commander (武将) (born [[1189]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 10th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1839]] [[December 10]]） – {{ill|Matsudaira Saiatsu|ja|松平斉厚|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Saiatsu|qq=}}, a daimyō (born [[1783]]). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 3rd year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1856]] [[December 2]]） – {{ill|Ashidai Hirokun|ja|足代弘訓|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashidai Hirokun|qq=}}, a kokugakuist (born [[1785]]). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 2nd year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1869]] [[December 7]]） – [[:en:Ōmura Masujirō|Ōmura Masujirō]], a military scholar (born [[1824]]).
