r ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1827|en|1827|WD=Q7008|lt=1827|1=1827}} {{ill|December 22|en|December 22|WD=Q2636|lt=December 22|1=December 22}}） – {{ill|Saisho Atsushi|en|Saisho Atsushi|WD=Q11596265|lt=Zeisho Atsu|1=Saisho Atsushi}}, a samurai and bureaucrat (died {{ill|1910|en|1910|WD=Q2075|lt=1910|1=1910}}). * Bunsei 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1830|en|1830|WD=Q7576|lt=1830|1=1830}} {{ill|December 19|en|December 19|WD=Q2451|lt=December 19|1=December 19}}） – {{ill|Sakakibara Kenkichi|en|Sakakibara Kenkichi|WD=Q933966|lt=Sakakibara Kanekichi|1=Sakakibara Kenkichi}}, a retainer (幕臣) and practitioner of {{ill|Kenjutsu|en|Kenjutsu|WD=Q249608|lt=Kenjutsu|1=Kenjutsu}} (died {{ill|1894|en|1894|WD=Q7843|lt=1894|1=1894}}).
